description: This Chainlink VRF common Parvati purrs with a rating of 37, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 74, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Leverage for East, Box for South, and Leverage for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40372-86462-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [74 Votes, Common]
